    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained by its single owner since day one. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster with zero scratches, dents, or chips, while the interior still smells new and shows no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly with a complete service history and all maintenance up to date. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
